news.title: Insomniacs partners with Salesforce to launch India’s largest AI-ready real estate tech ecosystem with 14 products across residential, commercial & redevelopment
news.para: Insomniacs, a leading real estate marketing and technology firm in India, has partnered with Salesforce to introduce an AI-ready suite of digital solutions for the real estate sector. This collaboration aims to provide developers with faster implementation, cost-effectiveness, and deep domain expertise.

news.title: Greater Patna to be developed on NCR model; metro rail operations to begin this month, says minister
news.para: Bihar is set for urban expansion with Greater Patna mirroring Delhi's NCR through land pooling, announced Minister Jibesh Mishra. The Patna Metro's priority corridor is slated for inauguration this month, potentially by PM Modi. Nine satellite towns are planned to decongest cities, alongside efforts to achieve garbage-free urban areas by 2027.

news.title: SC dismisses ED appeal in sand mining case in Tamil Nadu
news.para: The Supreme Court supported the Madras High Court's decision. It stopped the Enforcement Directorate's (ED) investigation. The case involved a suspected sand mining scam in Tamil Nadu. The ED had seized properties. The court said the ED needed a solid case. It needed proof of a crime before acting under the PMLA. The ED's actions were deemed baseless.
